item.description:
It's looking like 3+ feet on Sunday. Plus, the next few days are going to be killer so I'm thinking we should catch some nice waves Sunday afternoon.

Jenness is my favorite NH beach. my email is dvrocco82@gmail.com is have any questions.

I wear a black hooded suit and have a white bic hard top (look for the guy who resembles and overfed seal that can't paddle and rides a beginner board).

Jenness is in Rye NH right on Ocean Boulevard across from Summer Sessions. I hope this map location is accurate.

I'll be sitting on the beach (it's pretty small) between 12 and 1215. Otherwise, look for me in the water. ttyl
item.name: Surf Jenness Beach NH
